    <item>
      <title>李克强总理称中国将把澳大利亚纳入签证豁免计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/china-to-add-australia-to-visa-waiver-program-premier-li-qiang-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国务院总理李强在堪培拉会见澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴尼斯后宣布，中国将把澳大利亚纳入中国签证豁免计划，这是两国关系回暖的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/china-to-add-australia-to-visa-waiver-program-premier-li-qiang-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 03:31:06 GMT</pubDate>
